\": \"Not if Tebogo can help it.\", \"from\": 2424, \"to\": 2450, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tebogo\", \"from\": 2431, \"to\": 2437}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 21-year-old Botswanan has a stack of age-group records including the fastest 200m time ever by a teenager.\", \"from\": 2451, \"to\": 2561, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The 21-year-old Botswanan\", \"from\": 2451, \"to\": 2476}, {\"ngram\": \"a stack\", \"from\": 2481, \"to\": 2488}, {\"ngram\": \"age-group records\", \"from\": 2492, \"to\": 2509}, {\"ngram\": \"the fastest 200m time\", \"from\": 2520, \"to\": 2541}, {\"ngram\": \"a teenager\", \"from\": 2550, \"to\": 2560}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was the only man in these three semi-finals to run under 20 seconds, clocking 19.96 sec at a breeze, and his personal best of 19.50 could trouble Lyles, especially if the American gets a sluggish start.\", \"from\": 2562, \"to\": 2767, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2711, \"end\": 2716, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.9999999704123188, \"rank\": 2.396090673831499e-08, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\"}, {\"begin\": 2736, \"end\": 2744, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9960229643563171, \"rank\": 0.003991968724832558, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the only man\", \"from\": 2569, \"to\": 2581}, {\"ngram\": \"these three semi\", \"from\": 2585, \"to\": 2601}, {\"ngram\": \"finals\", \"from\": 2602, \"to\": 2608}, {\"ngram\": \"20 seconds\", \"from\": 2622, \"to\": 2632}, {\"ngram\": \"19.96 sec\", \"from\": 2643, \"to\": 2652}, {\"ngram\": \"a breeze\", \"from\": 2656, \"to\": 2664}, {\"ngram\": \"a sluggish start\", \"from\": 2750, \"to\": 2766}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tebogo finished only sixth in the 100m final but the longer distance is about hitting maximum speed and maintaining it, and here he is in his element.\", \"from\": 2769, \"to\": 2919, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tebogo\", \"from\": 2769, \"to\": 2775}, {\"ngram\": \"the 100m\", \"from\": 2799, \"to\": 2807}, {\"ngram\": \"the longer distance\", \"from\": 2818, \"to\": 2837}, {\"ngram\": \"maximum speed\", \"from\": 2855, \"to\": 2868}, {\"ngram\": \"his element\", \"from\": 2907, \"to\": 2918}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His top speed of 27.92mph was higher than all of the other 100m finalists (Lyles ranked second with 27.84mph).\", \"from\": 2920, \"to\": 3030, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2995, \"end\": 3000, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.9999999704123188, \"rank\": 2.396090673831499e-08, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His top speed\", \"from\": 2920, \"to\": 2933}, {\"ngram\": \"27.92mph\", \"from\": 2937, \"to\": 2945}, {\"ngram\": \"the other 100m finalists\", \"from\": 2969, \"to\": 2993}, {\"ngram\": \"27.84mph\", \"from\": 3020, \"to\": 3028}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The 100m, it's more of a tactical race,\\\" Tebogo said.\", \"from\": 3032, \"to\": 3086, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a tactical race\", \"from\": 3056, \"to\": 3071}, {\"ngram\": \"Tebogo\", \"from\": 3074, \"to\": 3080}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You have to get everything correct from the block, to your running, even timing your dip.\", \"from\": 3087, \"to\": 3177, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 3104, \"to\": 3114}, {\"ngram\": \"the block\", \"from\": 3128, \"to\": 3137},